{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, to improve the perceptions of PEU, which in turn increases the perception of enjoyment and usefulness, it is crucial to build user-friendly interfaces for metaverse-based learning platforms and ensure their stability and dependability in operation.",
    "Utilizing the metaverse in education necessitates the availability of high-quality infrastructure tailored to common learning practices.",
    "The hardware and software designs and frameworks of the metaverse serve as the basis for educational activities.",
    "Multiple variables, including accessibility, safety, humanity, trust, educational capacity, and cognitive traits of students, should be included in the metaverse design for higher education administrators, instructors, and students.",
    "Additionally, special emphasis must be placed on education's unique and extra design elements."
  ]
}